response.text:
Here’s a TekAutomate Steps UI flow for your production test on a Tektronix MSO4/5/6 Series scope. This flow:

1. Connects to the scope.
2. Resets the instrument.
3. Configures CH1 (1V/div, DC coupling) and CH2 (500mV/div, AC coupling).
4. Sets edge trigger on CH1, rising edge, 1V level.
5. Sets acquisition mode to average, 64 waveforms.
6. Adds measurements: frequency, amplitude, pk2pk, overshoot on CH1.
7. Queries all measurement results.
8. Error check.
9. Saves setup, waveform, and screenshot.
10. Disconnects.

```json
{
  "steps": [
    {
      "type": "connect",
      "id": "connect_scope",
      "label": "Connect to Scope"
    },
    {
      "type": "write",
      "id": "reset_scope",
      "label": "Reset Instrument",
      "params": {
        "command": "*RST"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "write",
      "id": "ch1_scale",
      "label": "Set CH1 1V/div, DC",
      "params": {
        "command": "CH1:SCAle 1"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "write",
      "id": "ch1_coupling",
      "label": "Set CH1 Coupling DC",
      "params": {
        "command": "CH1:COUPling DC"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "write",
      "id": "ch2_scale",
      "label": "Set CH2 500mV/div, AC",
      "params": {
        "command": "CH2:SCAle 0.5"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "write",
      "id": "ch2_coupling",
      "label": "Set CH2 Coupling AC",
      "params": {
        "command": "CH2:COUPling AC"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "write",
      "id": "trigger_edge",
      "label": "Set Edge Trigger CH1 Rising 1V",
      "params": {
        "command": "TRIGger:A:TYPe EDGE;:TRIGger:A:EDGE:SOUrce CH1;:TRIGger:A:EDGE:SLOpe RISing;:TRIGger:A:LEVel:CH1 1"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "write",
      "id": "acq_mode_avg",
      "label": "Set Acquisition Mode: Average 64",
      "params": {
        "command": "ACQuire:MODe AVErage;:ACQuire:NUMAVg 64"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "write",
      "id": "add_meas_freq",
      "label": "Add Frequency Measurement CH1",
      "params": {
        "command": "MEASUrement:ADDMeas FREQ,CH1"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "write",
      "id": "add_meas_ampl",
      "label": "Add Amplitude Measurement CH1",
      "params": {
        "command": "MEASUrement:ADDMeas AMPL,CH1"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "write",
      "id": "add_meas_pk2pk",
      "label": "Add Pk2Pk Measurement CH1",
      "params": {
        "command": "MEASUrement:ADDMeas PK2PK,CH1"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "write",
      "id": "add_meas_overshoot",
      "label": "Add Overshoot Measurement CH1",
      "params": {
        "command": "MEASUrement:ADDMeas OVERShoot,CH1"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "query",
      "id": "query_meas_freq",
      "label": "Query Frequency Result",
      "params": {
        "command": "MEASUrement:MEAS1:RESUlts:CURRent:VALue?"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "query",
      "id": "query_meas_ampl",
      "label": "Query Amplitude Result",
      "params": {
        "command": "MEASUrement:MEAS2:RESUlts:CURRent:VALue?"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "query",
      "id": "query_meas_pk2pk",
      "label": "Query Pk2Pk Result",
      "params": {
        "command": "MEASUrement:MEAS3:RESUlts:CURRent:VALue?"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "query",
      "id": "query_meas_overshoot",
      "label": "Query Overshoot Result",
      "params": {
        "command": "MEASUrement:MEAS4:RESUlts:CURRent:VALue?"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "error_check",
      "id": "error_check",
      "label": "Error Check"
    },
    {
      "type": "save_waveform",
      "id": "save_waveform",
      "label": "Save Waveform",
      "params": {
        "channel": "CH1",
        "filename": "waveform_ch1.csv"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "recall",
      "id": "save_setup",
      "label": "Save Setup",
      "params": {
        "action": "save",
        "filename": "scope_setup.set"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "save_screenshot",
      "id": "save_screenshot",
      "label": "Save Screenshot",
      "params": {
        "filename": "scope_screenshot.png"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "disconnect",
      "id": "disconnect_scope",
      "label": "Disconnect from Scope"
    }
  ]
}
```

Let me know if you want to adjust filenames, add comments, or further customize the flow!

